products.desc: Dell XPS eXtreme Performance System is a line of consumer-oriented high-end laptop and desktop computers manufactured by Dell

reviews.review: This unit got what I wanted. Display quality is to be seen to be believed. Keyboard-good. Trackpad-great. Battery Life, great. Number of ports-a pleasant surprise. SSD storage of 512 GB is more than what I required. Yet, Apple MacBook in aluminium stands out, in terms of looks. This LG 14 incher in black will not
I purchased this machine last week,the display is awesome same as LG OLED panels, very lightweight, fast in response, easy to read and write, touch pad is smooth.
